    "These results suggest that the participant size of 20 was acceptable for our evaluation study.",
    "Another relevant concern is that cultural and ethnic biases in the application of facial features.",
    "However, focusing on a single culture and ethnicity, such as Japan, can be beneficial for ensuring diversity and representativeness within this scale.",
